trans-unit.source: Provides static methods and properties for <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 為 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> 物件提供靜態方法和屬性。

trans-unit.source: All methods of this class are called by passing in a reference to the object that is requesting access to the method.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的所有方法都是透過將參考傳入要求存取方法的物件來進行呼叫。

trans-unit.source: This class belongs to the built-in object model category.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別屬於內建物件模型分類。

trans-unit.source: A static instance of the parent class of this class.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別之父類別的靜態執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the type of this class.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別型別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanPrototype" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanPrototype" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to a prototype-based object that is using this prototype.
trans-unit.target: 取得使用這個原型之原型架構物件的參考。

trans-unit.source: A reference to a prototype-based object.
The object that this method is acting upon.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法執行位置的物件。

trans-unit.source: Creates a string representation of the specified object by using the <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Convert" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 使用 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Convert" /> 類別建立指定之物件的字串表示。

trans-unit.source: A string representation of <paramref name="thisob" /> that is created by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Convert" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 由 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Convert" /> 類別所建立之 <paramref name="thisob" /> 的字串表示。

trans-unit.source: The object that this method is acting upon.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法執行位置的物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns the specified object as a <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> or a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: 將指定的物件傳回為 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> 或 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="thisob" /> as a <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> or a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="thisob" /> 做為 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> 或 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />。
